[A more likely reason for the present high incidence of measles in Ukraine is past deficiencies in the provision of comprehensive vaccine coverage throughout all regions of UKraine. Maps showing the administrative regions of Ukraine can be found at http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/ukraine/maps.htm. - Mod.CP]

